        Builds the binary expression, happening at the given location in the program.
        Parameters:
        cfg - the cfg that this statement belongs to
        sourceFile - the source file where this statement happens. If unknown, use null
        line - the line number where this statement happens in the source file. If unknown, use -1
        col - the column where this statement happens in the source file. If unknown, use -1
        left - the left hand-side of the expression
        right - the right hand-side of the expression
